						<div class="postbody">I have an idea of how to add hi-res mode.  Use Mode-0 with psuedo-hi-res with BG0 and BG2 on main-screen, and BG1 and BG3 on sub-screen.  BG2 and BG3 would have a &quot;dot-interlaced&quot; action screen and the HUB background, whereas BG0 and BG1 will be used for the HUB font.  I don't know if the FX-chip is fast enough to calculate the most convenient set of color palettes for each tile though.</div>

