						<div class="postbody">Oh, so you mean there's going to be more than 128 bullets on screen at the same time ?!<br />Even if that's the case, how's the CPU going to handle them ?<br /><br />If you require the Super-FX chip I definitely can't test it, as the Super Power Pak only supports no chip or the DSP-1. I don't know how much the DSP-1 helps at rendering stuff on the screen, but I don't think it does help at all.<br /><br />You can't have mode 7 and another BG, period. However, you could simulate mode-7 effets without using mdoe 7 at all. Especially if you have a Super-FX chip.</div>

